metadata.name: The 0x0.Art NFT #1
metadata.description: The [0x0.Art](https://0x0.art) utility token. This NFT provides access to the 1% royalities and 1% fees [pool](https://pool.0x0.art). Every NFT owner will have access to create its own artwork, convert it to NFT, claim for relief printed version and more other benefits. Check available NFT`s benefits, balance or withdraw it on [token admin area](https://pool.0x0.art/1).
